    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera is powered by the 3.6L M96 flat-six, featuring VarioCam Plus for optimized valve timing and lift. Power is delivered via a G96 6-speed manual transaxle, ensuring a direct mechanical connection. The chassis benefits from a multi-link rear suspension and MacPherson struts, providing excellent kinematic stability. Notable maintenance includes a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh RMS, mitigating common failure points in this displacement class. The braking system utilizes four-piston monobloc calipers for superior heat dissipation. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain exhibits strong compression and smooth gear synchronization, making this a mechanically sound driver's car.",
