    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained sports sedan offers a perfect balance of exhilarating performance and daily reliability. The exterior, finished in a deep metallic charcoal, retains a brilliant luster, though it shows a few minor stone chips on the front valence consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and free of cracks, the dashboard is pristine, and every electronic feature\u2014from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this vehicle stands out with a comprehensive service history, a recently serviced transmission, and a set of high-performance tires with plenty of tread remaining. It drives straight, brakes firmly, and offers the tight, responsive handling you expect from a well-cared-for machine. It is a turn-key example, ready for its next enthusiast owner.",
      "price": 36500.0,
